data.description: This gorgeous 6 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms home awaits for you and your family to come and enjoy!!  When you turn the doorknob you will see a foyer with hardwood flooring, an immaculate dining room with trey ceilings and hardwood flooring; Great room w/ fireplace.  Fresh paint and new carpet throughout the home and new roof. Come and enjoy a large and inviting kitchen with an oversized island and granite countertops along with eat in area too!!! The master bedroom, master bathroom with walk-in closet, laundry room; and 1/2 bath all located on the main flooring. This home has 4 huge bedrooms upstairs plus a over-sized bonus room with a closet (6th bedroom) above the finished 2 car garage. Large fenced in backyard. Don't sleep on this home it is ready for your family to move in today!!!!
